NAME

    Dist::Zilla::MintingProfile::AlienBuild - A minimal Dist::Zilla minting
    profile for Aliens

VERSION

    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS

     dzil new -P AlienBuild Alien::libfoo

DESCRIPTION

    This is a Dist::Zilla minting profile for creating Alien distributions
    based on the Alien::Build framework. It uses a reasonable template and
    the [@Starter] or [@Starter::Git] bundle plus the [AlienBuild] plugin.

SEE ALSO

    Alien

    Alien::Build

    alienfile

    [@Starter]

    [@Starter::Git]

    [AlienBuild]

